"""
DeltaTerminal Production Dashboard — Institutional-Grade Scanner
=================================================================
Phase 16: Compact tab-based layout with 9 tabs.
Preserves all verified forensic fixes. Only UI/monitoring/analytics improvements.

Architecture:
  - Top Status Bar (always visible)
  - 8 KPI Cards
  - 9 Tabs: Dashboard | Signals | Pipeline | Checklist | Orderflow | Market | Performance | Audit | Debug
  - Footer Status

DO NOT MODIFY: Emission Engine, Directional Cap, Session Fix, Checklist Fix, Signal Generator
"""
